&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://c5.staticflickr.com/8/7078/26967950180_24f7cc927f_b.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(24, 55, 120); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; width: 574px; height: 844px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;◎片　　名　睡在我上铺的兄弟&lt;/p&gt;
